Whenever I'm having really high anxiety, I listen to "I'm Scared" to remind myself that I'm not alone and I'm not going crazy, and then after that I listen to "Fly Around" because your voice in that song is so soothing and the song in general has a really nice feel to it and it calms me down and sometimes even helps me fall asleep at night.
